<p>Hi Aaron,</p>

<p>While I struggle with the practical implications of your thoughts here, I can&#8217;t argue much with the logic behind them.</p>

<p>I wonder, who is talking about the relationship between the &#8220;logic&#8221; of our actions regarding society, and the &#8220;effects&#8221; of those action? Perhaps I&#8217;m getting at this question: on what basis should we evaluate our actions re: society? Logic? Emotion? Pragmatism? Social Darwinism?</p>

<p>Thanks for sharing your Thoughts&#8230;</p>

<p>&#8212;Steve</p>

