<p>I&#8217;m not trying to control a person through money, I&#8217;m trying to control my own money, which I work to earn.  I don&#8217;t think I&#8217;m unreasonable for trying to direct the flow of my own money.</p>

<p>I think you have a drastically different view on the ownership of money than I do.</p>

<p class="posted">posted by <a rel="nofollow" href="http://subwindow.com">Erik Peterson</a>
 on April 20, 2008 <a href="moneycontrol#c8" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
